records.nl_statement: Prove that if $f(x)$ and $g(x)$ are polynomials with rational coefficients whose product $f(x) g(x)$ has integer coefficients, then the product of any coefficient of $g(x)$ with any coefficient of $f(x)$ is an integer.
records.lean_header:
import Mathlib

open Fintype Subgroup Set Polynomial Ideal
open scoped BigOperators
